      body("All six defined success criteria are met within a zero-cost deployment architecture, demonstrating that research-grade AI governance — encompassing explainability, fairness, and transparency — can be operationalized in user-facing production applications without prohibitive infrastructure investment. The evaluation results, validated through structured UAT with real users, confirm measurable improvements in matching accuracy, demographic parity, and user comprehension of AI-generated decisions."),
